query:
SELECT DISTINCT ipAddress, COUNT(*) as count 
FROM webhook_logs 
WHERE DATE(createdAt) >= DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 30 DAY)
GROUP BY ipAddress
ORDER BY count DESC
LIMIT 20;
